            "textpurpose":"Didactics",
            "textentryhtml":"Round, 5.1 cm. diam. gold design of Mao going to Anyuan. Young Mao, looking windswept, in full scholar robe, standing on rocky ground, with gold mountaintops in distance, brush/shrubs to the left of the figure on the same ground he stands on; carrying an umbrella in right hand, tip down, with right arm swung slightly behind, left arm swinging freely with fist clenched. Has gold edging that doesn’t wrap onto the front face of the badge.\r\nBack: matte burgundy pain (?).  “永远忠于毛主席 / 北京  光华”\r\nCONDITION: vertical scratches on left side of robe.\r\n",
